data.description: Welcome to 521 NW 9th, snuggled on an enchanting corner lot in a beautiful North Hill Location. This nicely appointed jewel-box is super sharp and boasts an extensive remodel to include, new roof, new windows, new drywall, modern trims, stylish luxury vinyl plank floors, attractive  light fixtures, water heater and new sewer line to the street.  The efficient kitchen features abundant cabinetry, newer countertops, and a well placed dining area with access to the laundry room. Outside you find a newer fenced yard, expansive BBQ deck and large storage garage.  All the work is done! Location! Sharp!, Value!
